<h2 class="bold font-l">Backdoor Code: THE BEAST</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Mari deactivates Unit-02's restrictors, transforming the Eva into a monster and putting her life in danger to get an edge. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DeadlyUpgrade" class='trope-example-link'>Deadly Upgrade</a></p>
